Package: GeneNMF
Type: Package
Title: Non-negative matrix factorization for single-cell omics
Version: 0.3.3
Authors@R: c(
  person('Massimo', 'Andreatta',
    email = 'massimo.andreatta@unil.ch',
    role = c('aut','cre'),
    comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0002-8036-2647'))
  )
Description: A collection of methods to extract gene programs from single-cell gene expression data using non-negative matrix factorization (NMF). It contains functions to directly interact with the Seurat toolkit and derive interpretable gene program signatures.
